Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:22.74,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}たとえまだ届かなくたって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:28.22,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}「ありがとう」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:26.75,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}都说太阳总会升起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:30.95,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}但不升起也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:33.88,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}想隐藏的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:36.71,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}想忘却的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:41.61,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}会被太阳照得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.48,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}寻找着流星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:47.00,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}独自彷徨着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:54.84,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}直到与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:23:01.85,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}在天空闪烁的那颗星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:07.25,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}照亮了希望之路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:12.07,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}不再迷茫 径直向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:18.45,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}跨过漆黑的夜晚 追随着祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:22.74,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}即使还传达不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.90,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}也想说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:28.22,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\c&HE92EFD&\bord0}「谢谢」
